{"tid":2490632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實移民","createTime":"2021-04-15T18:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T19:15:55.000Z","uid":232308,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"78a7d61ebb0b9ce68b5832d79e3316a8e115b80f","tid":2490632,"uid":232308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T18:03:35.000Z","msg":"大量流失資金同人材係攬炒最重要嘅一步<br />\n即係要好多人移民<br />\n<br />\n但其實係好難成功<br />\n因為當香港人走<br />\n政府就繼續放大陸人落嚟<br />\n結果只不過係將呢度變成大陸<br />\n<br />\n問題係唔走都係死路一條<br />\n咁走唔到可以點<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知<br />\n搞到緬甸咁咪冇人敢黎住<br />\n但係咪真係得<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知<br />\n我淨係知要有好多人留低先做到"},{"pid":"705ee63a6fb266ac721a5ac23b7fe7e5d3c56d2e","tid":2490632,"uid":232308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T18:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d459cf4abc4b0ada8b3e40750d8816963f302d","tid":2490632,"uid":232308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T18:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a475736f44844cc38ac41757520c8ff3dca50c4c","tid":2490632,"uid":232308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T18:40:05.000Z","msg":"點解負評呀<br />\n講嚟聽吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7106ebe77e0acc7e57d8374be38db3883eefa4e8","tid":2490632,"uid":339874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T18:45:21.000Z","msg":"無既 走唔走都150人一日（其實唔止）<br />\n所以香港已死 尤其中共連做戲都唔做<br />\n移民 亦都係表態既一種"},{"pid":"9f620db8057a78b66c4d24500631880f21d9675e","tid":2490632,"uid":262358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T18:47:13.000Z","msg":"前幾日有個po講得啱<br />\n唔好講咩對香港有感情 香港係上年已經死左<br />\n有錢嘅就走 無錢嘅搵多幾年錢都好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee65369bfaaa26de9b9f5d756ec0224a37b840c","tid":2490632,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T19:01:52.000Z","msg":"為信念 堅守這要塞<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf3F4eDsrerkp1Xdj6b7sbST1wZRq45pTM8H5MTFkNoB6?filename=p8FQGWO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp8FQGWO.gif&h=77ff4844&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a15eb7b373b3f5aedfce827dd701320185ece4c","tid":2490632,"uid":82717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T19:15:55.000Z","msg":"如果無人敢黎香港 咁嗰個香港又係唔係你想要嘅香港？"}]}